75
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,959
Gu and Jiang

76
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,360
broke up.

77
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,280
Here's your opportunity

78
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,440
