283
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:32,360
Just call her Xiu.

284
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,200
Nice to meet you, Xiu.

285
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:45,440
[Unit 53082 of People's Liberation Army]

286
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:43,600
Really?

287
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,400
